data.description: Ready for a new owner! Situated on nearly half an acre and conveniently located across from the park, 40 Wendy Lane is a clean, charming home with 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and an attached 1-car garage. This home received an update throughout in 2019 with new siding, wooden cabinetry, flooring, interior paint, updated electrical panel, on-demand hot water system/boiler and more. With a new roof and fencing completed in 2022, this home is not only visually appealing but also well-maintained and very clean for a new owner. The back yard is roomy enough for pets, a large garden area or additional storage. This home effortlessly combines comfort, convenience and a picturesque setting on a quiet street. Call your favorite real estate professional today for a tour of this property.
